OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774519535
OL,3,C'With Him, nothing will be
OL,4,Cimpossible': New Archbishop of
OL,5,CCanterbury installed
OL,7,FThe first female Archbishop of
OL,8,FCanterbury has said "nothing is
OL,9,Fimpossible" with the help of God, as
OL,10,Fshe gave a sermon to an audience
OL,11,Fincluding the Prince and Princess of
OL,12,FWales and the Prime Minister.
OL,14,FSpeaking as she was installed as the
OL,15,Fmost senior Archbishop in the Church
OL,16,Fof England, Dame Sarah Mullally
OL,17,Fconcluded her address by stating "may
OL,18,Fwe have the audacity to believe in the
OL,19,Fpromises of God, for with Him, nothing
OL,20,Fwill be impossible."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
