PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774519535
OL,3,C'With Him, nothing will be
OL,4,Cimpossible': New Archbishop of
OL,5,CCanterbury installed
OL,7,FDame Sarah is the first woman to hold
OL,8,Fthe role in its 1,400-year history.
OL,10,FShe arrived in Canterbury on Sunday
OL,11,Ffollowing the end of a six-day walking
OL,12,Fpilgrimage from London, telling those
OL,13,Fshe greeted that she was "very
OL,14,Frelieved" to complete the 87-mile
OL,15,Fjourney.
OL,17,FEarlier in her sermon, Dame Sarah
OL,18,Fapologised for the "hurt" experienced
OL,19,Fby those who were harmed in Christian
OL,20,Fcommunities.
OL,26,@uD@ZOUvD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
