PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774519535
OL,3,C'With Him, nothing will be
OL,4,Cimpossible': New Archbishop of
OL,5,CCanterbury installed
OL,7,FShe said: "In a world already torn by
OL,8,Fconflict, suffering, and division, we
OL,9,Fmust also acknowledge the hurt that
OL,10,Fexists much closer to home.
OL,12,F"We must not overlook or minimise the
OL,13,Fpain experienced by those who have
OL,14,Fbeen harmed through the actions,
OL,15,Finactions, or failures of those in our
OL,16,Fown Christian communities.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
