PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774519535
OL,3,C'With Him, nothing will be
OL,4,Cimpossible': New Archbishop of
OL,5,CCanterbury installed
OL,7,F"Today, and every day, we hold victims
OL,8,Fand survivors in our hearts and in our
OL,9,Fprayers, and we must remain committed
OL,10,Fto truth, compassion, justice and
OL,11,Faction."
OL,13,FIt comes after the previous Archbishop
OL,14,FJustin Welby resigned over failures in
OL,15,Fhandling a Church of England abuse
OL,16,Fscandal.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
