PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774519535
OL,3,C'With Him, nothing will be
OL,4,Cimpossible': New Archbishop of
OL,5,CCanterbury installed
OL,7,FDuring her sermon Dame Sarah also
OL,8,Frecited a prayer written for her
OL,9,Fpilgrimage by Student Chaplains at the
OL,10,FArchbishop's School in Canterbury,
OL,11,Fwhich talked of being "gentle and
OL,12,Fhumble" and being able to "share the
OL,13,FGospel with joy".
OL,15,FThe Archbishop reflected too on her
OL,16,Fown teenage years and how she could
OL,17,Fnot have have predicted the role she
OL,18,Fnow takes on.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
