PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774519535
OL,3,C'With Him, nothing will be
OL,4,Cimpossible': New Archbishop of
OL,5,CCanterbury installed
OL,7,FShe said: "As I look back over my life
OL,8,F` at the teenage Sarah, who put her
OL,9,Ffaith in God and made a commitment to
OL,10,Ffollow Jesus. I could never have
OL,11,Fimagined the future that lay ahead,
OL,12,Fand certainly not the ministry to
OL,13,Fwhich I am now called."
OL,15,FOne of the most symbolic moments of
OL,16,Fthe ceremony came when Dame Sarah
OL,17,Fbanged three times on the West Door of
OL,18,Fthe Cathedral, seeking permission to
OL,19,Fenter.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774519535
OL,3,C'With Him, nothing will be
OL,4,Cimpossible': New Archbishop of
OL,5,CCanterbury installed
OL,7,FThe new Archbishop also exchanged
OL,8,Fwords with children from John Wallis
OL,9,FAcademy in Ashford, where she promised
OL,10,Fto "proclaim the love of Christ and
OL,11,Fwith you to worship and love him with
OL,12,Fheart and soul, mind and strength"
OL,14,FThe African Choir of Norfolk sang at
OL,15,Fthe service, and the Archbishop was
OL,16,Falso presented with a special crosier.
OL,18,FThere were representatives from the
OL,19,FVatican at the service, who attended
OL,20,Falongside leaders of the Roman
OL,21,FCatholic Church from across the UK
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
