OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774519535
OL,3,C'With Him, nothing will be
OL,4,Cimpossible': New Archbishop of
OL,5,CCanterbury installed
OL,7,FThe Orthodox and Oriental Orthodox
OL,8,FChurches, as well as other large
OL,9,FChristian denominations, were also
OL,10,Frepresented.
OL,12,FDame Sarah was a chief nursing officer
OL,13,Fin England before she was ordained,
OL,14,Fwith NHS nurses and carers working in
OL,15,Fhospitals and hospices in Canterbury
OL,16,Fbeing invited to attend the ceremony.
OL,18,FAfter the service, the Archbishop then
OL,19,Fblessed the City and Diocese of
OL,20,FCanterbury and the County of Kent,
OL,21,F"now and in the years to come".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
